    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 120120.0,
      "end_time": 122340.0,
      "text": "It's like when we live in a foreign country,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 122340.0,
      "end_time": 124640.0,
      "text": "we soon pick up the language."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 124640.0,
      "end_time": 126400.0,
      "text": "You must be thinking now..."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 126400.0,
      "end_time": 128440.0,
      "text": "Great! Serena, You know what?"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 128440.0,
      "end_time": 130919.0,
      "text": "I cannot move to another country"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 130919.00000000001,
      "end_time": 134680.0,
      "text": "so I don't have an all-English environment."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 134680.0,
      "end_time": 138280.0,
      "text": "You can create the environment yourself."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 138280.0,
      "end_time": 139599.0,
      "text": "Here are some tips:"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 139599.0,
      "end_time": 142919.0,
      "text": "First, don't think that you have to learn"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 142919.0,
      "end_time": 147520.0,
      "text": "general English that you can use in all kinds of situations"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 147520.0,
      "end_time": 150960.0,
      "text": "like in three weeks or three months."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 150960.0,
      "end_time": 152840.0,
      "text": "It will be a long journey."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 152840.0,
      "end_time": 157300.0,
      "text": "You have to break it into small and actionable steps."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 157300.0,
      "end_time": 158220.0,
      "text": "For example,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 158220.0,
      "end_time": 159380.0,
      "text": "if you are a foodie,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 159380.0,
      "end_time": 163220.0,
      "text": "start with food, find interesting videos online about your"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 163220.0,
      "end_time": 167020.0,
      "text": "favorite food, pick up those words and use it immediately."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 167020.0,
      "end_time": 169880.0,
      "text": "By doing so you won't feel stressed out"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 169880.0,
      "end_time": 173300.0,
      "text": "because you only need a certain amount of vocabulary"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 173300.0,
      "end_time": 175560.0,
      "text": "to describe the items you like."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 175560.0,
      "end_time": 180660.0,
      "text": "That also means, you will be willing to practice on a daily basis."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 180660.0,
      "end_time": 182960.0,
      "text": "Second, let's talk about shadowing."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 182960.0,
      "end_time": 187220.0,
      "text": "I know you've heard that! But, did you do it right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 187220.0,
      "end_time": 189340.0,
      "text": "Why shadowing is helpful?"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 189340.0,
      "end_time": 192500.0,
      "text": "It's for us to have the connections"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 192500.0,
      "end_time": 197599.0,
      "text": "between the situation in the TV shows  and the spoken English"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 197599.0,
      "end_time": 203180.0,
      "text": "When you shadow, you not only learn what you're saying, you also have"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 203180.0,
      "end_time": 208319.0,
      "text": "to pretend that you are the actor or actress in the TV shows."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 208319.0,
      "end_time": 211319.0,
      "text": "That's what I did when I was in high school."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 211319.0,
      "end_time": 213840.0,
      "text": "For example, when the actor shouted:"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 213840.0,
      "end_time": 215819.0,
      "text": "I can't believe it."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 215819.0,
      "end_time": 216800.0,
      "text": "I would say"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 216800.0,
      "end_time": 218720.0,
      "text": "I can't believe it!"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 218720.0,
      "end_time": 222460.0,
      "text": "Why dramatic shadowing can help you"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
